'''澳大利亚兒童裸照風波'''是指2008年5月起[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]牽起的[[兒童|兒童]][[裸照|裸照]]爭議，事件中一位[[母親|母親]]替當時六歲的[[女兒|女兒]]拍下裸照，5年後在澳大利亚一場[[藝術|藝術]]攝影展中展出，照片以藝術手法展示女童[[裸體|裸體]]，當中只能看見[[臀部|臀部]]及[[乳頭|乳頭]]，未有展示女童[[性器官|性器官]]，但照片旋即被警方查封，主辦單位被調查是否涉及[[兒童色情|兒童色情]]。期後舉辦藝展的藝術[[雜誌|雜誌]]《Arts Monthly》在封面刊登裸照，抗議[[審查|審查]]制度。

事件在澳大利亚引起連串爭議。[[澳大利亞總理|澳大利亚總理]][[陸克文|陸克文]]形容難以接受這批照片，多個兒童保護組織亦批評這是兒童色情，但案中女童（當年12歲）對自己的照片被指為淫褻感到「極為冒犯」。<ref name=SMH.com>{{Cite web |url=http://news.smh.com.au/national/pm-very-rude-about-my-nude-photo-girl-20080707-32sh.html |title=PM very rude about my nude photo: girl |publisher=The Sydney Morning Herald |date=2008-07-07 |archivedate=2009-06-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090603062429/http://news.smh.com.au/national/pm-very-rude-about-my-nude-photo-girl-20080707-32sh.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>　

== 沿起 ==
2008年5月22日，澳大利亚[[攝影師|攝影師]]Bill Henson準備在[[新南威爾斯州|新南威爾斯州]]一間藝廊舉行攝影展，警方事前收到8人[[投訴|投訴]]指邀請函上有兒童裸照，攝影展被迫取消。<ref>{{cite news |last=Tovey |first=Josephine |coauthors=Kennedy, Les; Welch, Dylan |date=May 24, 2008 |title=Art obscenity charges |work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/arts/henson-finds-support-over-photos/2008/05/23/1211183097197.html |accessdate=2008-05-28 |archivedate=2008-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080713043449/http://www.smh.com.au/news/arts/henson-finds-support-over-photos/2008/05/23/1211183097197.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Gallery: Nude children exhibit shut |work=[[News.com.au|News.com.au]] |url=http://www.news.com.au/gallery/0,22056,5031912-5010140,00.html |accessdate=2008-05-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080525213842/http://www.news.com.au/gallery/0%2C22056%2C5031912-5010140%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-05-25 }}</ref>。同日，當地報章一名[[專欄作家|專欄作家]]Miranda Devine在報上嚴厲批評照片內容<ref>{{cite news |last=Devine |first=Miranda |date=2008-05-22 |title=Moral backlash over sexing up of our children |publisher=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |url=http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2008/05/21/1211182891875.html?page=3 |accessdate=2008-06-16 |archivedate=2016-03-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183127/http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2008/05/21/1211182891875.html?page=3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，引起民間關注。警方在查封照片時發現更多兒童裸照，並尋求指引了解照片有否違反當地的兒童保護條例。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aifs.gov.au/nch/resources/legislation/legislation.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-07-07 |archivedate=2009-07-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090711023525/http://www.aifs.gov.au/nch/resources/legislation/legislation.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

