5月23日，警方公布查封了數張照片，並正考慮控告相關人士發放淫褻（indecent）物品。<ref name="Kennedy">{{cite news |last=Kennedy |first=Les |date=May 23, 2008 |title=Henson show charges |work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/arts/henson-show-charges/2008/05/23/1211183060208.html |accessdate=2008-05-28 |archivedate=2018-05-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180515090830/https://www.smh.com.au/news/arts/henson-show-charges/2008/05/23/1211183060208.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這批照片在涉事的藝廊Roslyn Oxley9的網頁上移除。<ref name="roslynoxley9">{{cite web |title=Bell Henson, 2008 |work=Roslyn Oxley9 Gallery |url=http://www.roslynoxley9.com.au/artists/18/Bill_Henson/1098/ |accessdate=2008-05-28 |archivedate=2019-06-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612090912/https://www.roslynoxley9.com.au/artists/18/Bill_Henson/1098/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但《[[世紀報|世紀報]]》在5月25日刊登該報道時，在無[[马赛克_(影像处理)|打码]]情況下繼續公開部分照片<ref name="Elder">{{cite news |last=Elder |first=John |date=May 25, 2008 |title=The controversial career of Bill Henson |work=[[The_Age|The Age]] |url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/national/the-controversial-career-of-bill-henson/2008/05/24/1211183189567.html |accessdate=2008-05-28 |archivedate=2018-05-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517064002/https://www.theage.com.au/news/national/the-controversial-career-of-bill-henson/2008/05/24/1211183189567.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

事件擾釀至6月5日，當地政府宣布不會作出[[檢控|檢控]]<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20080609050237/http://au.news.yahoo.com/080606/21/1761j.html No charges for Henson</ref>，當天澳大利亚國家藝廊前總監Betty Churcher表示對政府的決定不覺得驚訝，因為把這種個案訴諸法庭是相當荒謬，「法庭不是決定甚麼叫藝術的地方」。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20080610145101/http://au.news.yahoo.com/080606/21/175vw.html 'Not surprising' no charges laid over NGA Henson collection] Retrieved on 2008-06-06.</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20080609050237/http://au.news.yahoo.com/080606/21/1761j.html No case against Henson: prosecutors] Retrieved on 2008-06-06.</ref>

有關爭議在7月再起波瀾，主辦該攝影展的雜誌《Arts Monthly》在封面刊登一幅兒童裸照抗議審查制度。該照片的主角是現年11歲的女孩Olympia Nelson，6歲時由母親拍下該照片。

